## Key Insight: Scramble-Realign Cycle
- 72% of aligner time is idle_align_scramble (no alignable targets)
- Only 7% is actual align_junction
- Bottleneck: many scrambled enemy junctions NOT within our alignment range
- Solution: prioritize scrambling enemy junctions within our network range

